---
// HomePage - Interface statique (données PocketBase)
---

<div class="min-h-screen bg-gradient-to-b from-white via-green-50/30 to-white">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-20">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <div>
        <h1 class="text-5xl mb-6 text-gray-900">
          VOS LUNETTES,
          <br />
          <span class="text-[#2C7319]">VOTRE STYLE</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
          Concevez vos lunettes personnalisées avec notre configurateur innovant.
        </p>
        <a 
          href="/configurator"
          class="inline-flex items-center bg-[#2C7319] hover:bg-[#3a9122] text-white px-8 py-6 rounded-full transition-all shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl hover:scale-105"
        >
          JE CRÉE MES LUNETTES
          <svg class="ml-2 w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6"></path>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
      
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
          <img 
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1663706933971-9f3d6b99c678?crop=entropy&cs=tinysrgb&fit=max&fm=jpg&q=80&w=1080"
            alt="Lunettes modernes"
            class="w-full h-[500px] object-cover"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Values Section -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-[#2C7319] to-[#3a9122] text-white py-16 my-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-center text-3xl mb-12 tracking-wide">NOS VALEURS</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-white/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 backdrop-blur-sm">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"></path>
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M2.458 12C3.732 7.943 7.523 5 12 5c4.478 0 8.268 2.943 9.542 7-1.274 4.057-5.064 7-9.542 7-4.477 0-8.268-2.943-9.542-7z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="mb-3 tracking-wide">Design unique</h3>
          <p class="text-green-50 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Créez des lunettes qui vous ressemblent vraiment avec notre configurateur intelligent.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-white/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 backdrop-blur-sm">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 3v4M3 5h4M6 17v4m-2-2h4m5-16l2.286 6.857L21 12l-5.714 2.143L13 21l-2.286-6.857L5 12l5.714-2.143L13 3z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="mb-3 tracking-wide">Simplicité d'usage</h3>
          <p class="text-green-50 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Un parcours fluide et intuitif pour concevoir vos lunettes en quelques clics.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How It Works -->
  <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-20">
    <h2 class="text-center text-3xl text-gray-900 mb-4">COMMENT ÇA MARCHE ?</h2>
    <p class="text-center text-gray-600 mb-16 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      Un processus simple et intuitif pour créer les lunettes parfaites en quelques étapes.
    </p>
    
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all">
        <div class="text-5xl text-[#2C7319] mb-4 opacity-20">01</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl mb-3 text-gray-900">Choisissez vos matériaux</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          Sélectionnez parmi notre gamme de matériaux nobles et durables pour créer votre monture.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all">
        <div class="text-5xl text-[#2C7319] mb-4 opacity-20">02</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl mb-3 text-gray-900">Personnalisez le design</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          Ajustez les dimensions, les formes et les couleurs pour un rendu unique et à votre image.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all">
        <div class="text-5xl text-[#2C7319] mb-4 opacity-20">03</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl mb-3 text-gray-900">Commandez et recevez</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          Validez votre création et recevez vos lunettes personnalisées.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-green-50 to-green-100 rounded-3xl p-12 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl text-gray-900 mb-4">PRÊT À CRÉER VOS LUNETTES ?</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8 text-lg">
        Lancez-vous dès maintenant dans l'aventure de la personnalisation
      </p>
      <a 
        href="/configurator"
        class="inline-block bg-[#2C7319] hover:bg-[#3a9122] text-white px-12 py-6 rounded-full transition-all shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl"
      >
        COMMENCER LA CRÉATION
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>
